Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.93,0:00:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The wind is warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May. When I wake up and open the window,\NI don't recoil from the wind anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.42,0:00:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rei Kiriyama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.50,0:00:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's my name.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In a small town by a big river,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is where I live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Class C-1, 5th dan. Eighteen years old.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.27,0:01:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Profession: Pro shogi player.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Setting Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:39.78,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KOMAHASHI PRIVATE HIGH SCHOOL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shogi Science Club activities\Nhave finally begun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SCIENCE LAB
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}Eisaku Noguchi\NThird-year high school student
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay if I look at the book?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}After School Shogi Science Club
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:02:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:02:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Rei Kiriyama\NProfession: Pro shogi player
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:03.05,LeftSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shogi\NScience\NClub
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}OOTA-KUN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get near the king as if to surround it, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}MUTTER MUTTER
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:05.27,LeftSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Former\NHomeroom\NTeacher
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:05.27,RightSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Faculty\NAdvisor\NTakashi\NHayashida
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For me, this is pretty much\Nmy first club activity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I could do this, but then\Nmy bishop would be captured, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SIGH
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SLUMP
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't realize defeat\Ncould be this painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I'm never subjected to such severe\N"wins" or "losses" in everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And even worse,\NI must declare the "loss" myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}With three pawns,\Nshift and slide the opponent's pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I read the book\Nand come up with a strategy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}A feisty knight will be eaten by a pawn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my opponent would most likely\Nattack me in a different way,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}The pawn under a gold general\Nis more solid than a rock
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Strike rooks and bishops from a distance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}Shogi Proverb Cards by Noguchi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,\NI even made shogi proverb cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:04:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if I come up with a plan, my opponent\Nwill have a countermeasure to my plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,forcing me to think of a countermeasure\Nto his countermeasures to my original plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bwaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! There's no end to it, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Well, no, there's no end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally your opponent\Nisn't going to go by the book,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so just be careful as you proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}ROOK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First, with Climbing Silver, your goal\Nis to promote your rook, so please aim for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you do that, try not to\Nlet any of your pieces be captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And after it's promoted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The ultimate goal\Nis to capture your opponent's king,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so you should surround that king\Nwith as many of your pieces as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:48.70,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SILVER GENERAL
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:49.66,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PROMOTED PAWN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got your back, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if I move a lot of my pieces like that,\NI'll be leaving my own castle wide open.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:53.71,RightSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BANG
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:55.46,RightSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BANG
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:57.21,RightSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BANG
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:04:59.00,RightSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BANG
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You noticed that, huh? You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}GROAN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey, meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give us the king-meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Lance - Pawn - Silver General - Promoted Pawn - Bishop
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...get our king!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Lance - Gold General - King - Gold General - Silver General
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because you only have\Na limited number of pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That being said, if you only defend,\Nyou won't be effective at attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}DASH
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is where I prove myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silver General, wait! Come back, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SNEAK SNEAK SNEAK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}TREMBLE TREMBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The balance between attacking and defending\Nis an eternal theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'll just have to play a lot\Nso you can remember things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not only from books, but these days\Nyou can play on the internet too,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so you can enjoy playing at home\Nin a relaxed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}POINT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you beat the crap out of this guy for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I'll lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should my next move be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make this guy pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please think on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? You're so cold, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You're a stinge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can you do this to your old teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cheating is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}FLAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}FLAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you allow your students to cheat on tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}NO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}NO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, right? You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to listen to reason right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not reason, it's the rules.\NYou're not a child, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's keep playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid of losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't play a lot,\Nyou can't get a feel for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to get used to losing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you stop getting frustrated at losing,\Nthen you'll stop studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Question! How strong do I have to become\Nbefore saying farewell to this frustration?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you get strong,\Nbut play with someone who's better, you'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, it's so frustrating it feels like\Nyour innards are turning upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It never ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's forever frustrating and forever painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}BLUNT
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Except when you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}WHISPER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The stronger you get,\Nthe more bitter defeat tastes when you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, the more time you spend on it,\Nthe more frustrating it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The more you progress,\Nthe more frustrated you'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have fun when you play shogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:19.69,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FREEZE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:19.69,DefaultRightH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,QUIVER\NQUIVER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*This background has metaphorical images as accompaniment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FREEZE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Kiriyama.\NH-How would you like some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's tear grass tea made with the tear grass\NI acquired from the field behind the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Noguchi, you really are serious about\Nself-sufficiency, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I also have coffee made with dandelion roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not science anymore, but agriculture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}STAGGER
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:11.74,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WOBBLE\NWOBBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's tear grass tea for you!\NSuch a pronounced diuretic effect. Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take too long, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Meijin Battle will be on TV from 4:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll be quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was five years ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he'd boarded the train without disguising\Nhimself, he would've been recognized.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So of course, I was fooled, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And thus 14 people...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}100 FAMOUS LAKES OF JAPAN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Aburasaka Pass is between\NFukui Prefecture and Gifu Prefecture.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama is already living his life\Nas a professional?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's already living in that harsh world\Nof "victories" and "defeats," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:09:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even the best player, Meijin Souya,\Nhas a winning rate of 70%.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He loses three out of ten matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}MEIJIN BATTLE\NTOUJI VS KUMAKURA\NSECOND MATCH
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He won the "Seven Crowns," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So they're broadcasting\Nhis match live today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's the second match\Nfor the Meijin Battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the first match,\Nhe lost to the challenger, Kumakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The stronger you get,\Nthe more bitter defeat tastes, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then when somebody at this level loses,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's going on in his mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the first day of the second match\Nfor the 69th Shogi Meijin Battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Let's begin with the two players\Nentering the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}Challenger\NKengo Kumakura\N9th-dan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At 8:53 am, the challenger,\NKengo Kumakura 9th-Dan, entered the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}Touji Souya\NMeijin
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:10:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}And then, at 8:55 am,\NMeijin Souya entered the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The match began at 9:00 am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In just a moment,\Nthe second match will begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Souya looks like he's having fun.\NI'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Souya will be coming for you\Nin the Kishou Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As the challenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scary. But I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Souya has a cute face,\Nbut he'll come to break my bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, scary, scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's because the casual moves\Nyou make mock your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mock? I'm always serious when I play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. I meant,\Nyou seriously mock your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I can win a slugfest,\Nthen I'll start throwing punches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But now it's tough on me physically.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm about to hit 60.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll probably croak in the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When your opponent goes all out,\Nyou don't get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you hit him with everything you've got,\Nhe returns your blows at the same level.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Souya is happy to have\Nan opponent like that in Kumakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And vice versa, Kumakura with Soya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're both thinking that their opponent
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is a toy that won't break\Nno matter how hard they spin it around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, these two make such a perfect picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It ran across my mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, Mr. Shimada...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}must be watching these two\Nfrom somewhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From a classroom dyed red by the setting sun,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the person on the screen...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...seemed to be slightly smiling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Setting Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ramune
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's eating with his hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, he killed three pieces of cake\Nin mere seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He gobbled them up, just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And his eyes were locked\Non the board the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such splendor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, this is an interesting scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right in the middle of a serious battle,\Nwith the combatants in kimonos,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,snacks would suddenly appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it's being broadcast across the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the brain is the biggest eater\Nof all the organs in the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And glucose is the\Nonly nourishment it can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In shogi, you need your brain\Nfiring on all cylinders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so, what is Souya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's supplementing the energy\Nin his brain directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How many sugar cubes was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And three slices of lemon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Citric acid to recover from fatigue\Nand sugar for brain energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's too straightforward!\NAs expected from a Meijin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}WOW WOW\NSO COOL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's so efficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These two are monsters!\NIn more meanings that one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you're stuck on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHOGI HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three pieces of cake, wolfed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kuma has some appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's already famous for it\Non these tournament broadcasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That appetite of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They always show the "snack time."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And Kuma can put away the booze too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the man who ate cakes\Nwhile emptying a bottle of sweet potato shochu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does that even go together? I bet it doesn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, we've got Souya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now there's a dull man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You thought they were\Nsugar cubes, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pure glucose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?\NThen he's just feeding his brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How bland can you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although that's just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they sell that now, in soft cubed form.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At drug stores and convenience stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know a lot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Souya asked me to pick some up,\Nwhen we were in Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He said he ate what he had,\Nand asked me to get more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoto? Oh, the Lion King Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With Shimada...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He must have used a lot of brain power\Nand stamina to take down Shimada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although at 4-0, he made it look easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess even the title-holder is desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}69th Meijin Battle\NSecond Match\NEnd
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So the brain is the "biggest eater," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kiriyama. Do you know\Nwhat ramune is made of?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Glucose and starch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Glucose?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And it's easy to make.\NWould you like to try making some?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The first day's broadcast is over anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We should have some ingredients left over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We did an experimental food sampler\Nfor last year's bazaar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Between natto, rice, and tear grass tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, all you guys do is eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's science. All part of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:17:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TODAY'S SCIENCE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Science in 20 Minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Homemade Ramune
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First, you sift finely-crushed glucose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then you put potato starch\Nand water in a beaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But only that would be bland,\Nso let's add some citric acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A sour flavor is refreshing in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And citric acid is also effective against fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}LITTLE BIT
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then you mix it and heat it up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all the citric acid you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even a miniscule amount like this\Nis extremely sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After that, you mix in the glucose little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}GLUCOSE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Knead it, knead it, and squeeze it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And we're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}BOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- What?\N- Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slice it into small pieces like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,let it dry naturally, and it's ready to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It hasn't hardened yet, but go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It really is ramune.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! So this is how ramune is made!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your delightful surprise\Nmakes the experiment worthwhile, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}WOW
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}WOW COOL
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}WOW COOL WOW
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}HAHAHA
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we make some\Nwith baking soda, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Baking soda?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sodium bicarbonate.\NIt's carbonic acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can make it fizzy like cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I try making some?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very nice, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you've come to appreciate\Nthe wonders of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is science?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.\NWhat else would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you go.\NOh, don't put in too much water.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There it is. Now mix, mix...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, about this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, are you actually\Nclumsy with this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}CITRIC ACID
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That might be a little too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- H-Huh?\N- You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was that too much water?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, are you a little kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are both of your hands\Nmoving in the same direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you can't draw a square with your right hand\Nwhile drawing a triangle with your left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Kiriyama.\NAll you have to do is add more glucose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- What?\N- You can save it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm participating in a club activity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm laughing and talking...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...at school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's give it a taste test.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ramune is sweet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and when I put it in my mouth, it falls apart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As it melted, I felt a lump in my throat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, the ones with the baking soda\Nare definitely the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, these are more refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I wasn't careful, it felt like\Nsomething was going to leak from my eyes,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I used every ounce of will to hold it in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, could I take this home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wrapped the remaining ramune\Nin a scrap of notebook paper,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and put it in my bag.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought Hina and Momo would enjoy it\Nif I shared some with them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll go visit them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll cross that bridge...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:21:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.90,0:22:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How to make ramune...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My club activities...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About Noguchi-senpai...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About Mr. Hayashida...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.08,0:22:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted to tell them...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.09,0:22:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...all about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.10,0:23:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.78,0:24:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fizzy! How is it, Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.49,0:24:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei and his friends made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.83,0:24:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I want to try making it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.54,0:24:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, could you teach me how?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.33,0:24:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.79,0:24:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fizzy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.01,0:24:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ramune
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:38.18,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 24
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.34,0:24:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why! Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.68,0:24:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is good. That's not good.\NAre you the one who decides that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.18,0:24:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are the embodiment of chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.48,0:24:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want neither of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.52,0:24:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think even Souya\Nknows what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.73,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh... Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.03,0:24:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to the next\N"March comes in like a lion".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.82,0:24:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, thank you!\NRamune is really delicious, huh?
